Various small scripts and tools

* vping.pl   - Console visualization for 'ping' command
* ttr.sh     - Tiny 'Unix Time' to 'Date' translation tool
* passgen.sh - Simple password generator
* shells.pl  - Analysis of user shell accounts
* sdu.sh     - Small tool for searching largest files and directories
* bsa.pl     - Brief system analysis tool (free space, TOP-n of CPU/MEM consuming processes, long running cron jobs, etc)
* uinfo.sh   - Quick information about Linux user (passwd, group, etc)
